The transport plane is returning home from the southern countries, the crew has stocked up on fruits so that the entire board is packed to capacity. They are accelerating along the runway. 500 meters to the end of the lane, there is no breakaway. 300 meters to the end of the lane, there is no breakaway. 100 meters to the end of the lane, separation. The plane begins to climb. The commander tells the navigator:
- Bl@, you could also grab a box of cherries...
